            "name": "rpd_ee_diff_challenge_body",
            "type": "textarea",
            "rows": 5,
            "default_value": "Three days of training at the district service center might check the box on state compliance, but most educators say that type of training, by itself, is ineffective and inconvenient.\n\nFully asynchronous training is more convenient, but doesn't always feature the collaboration and job-embedded practice that educators value, or need, especially with job-related stress and attrition at all-time highs.",
